## Project Structure

```
llm-finetuning-pipeline/
├── src/
│   ├── data/
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   ├── preprocessor.py       # Raw data cleaning & dedup
│   │   └── dataset_builder.py    # Instruction-tuning format builder
│   ├── training/
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   ├── config.py             # TrainingConfig dataclass
│   │   ├── trainer.py            # QLoRA trainer using TRL SFTTrainer
│   │   └── callbacks.py          # MLflow + early stopping callbacks
│   ├── evaluation/
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   └── evaluator.py          # ROUGE, F1, BERTScore evaluation
│   ├── serving/
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   └── inference.py          # FastAPI inference server
│   └── utils/
│       ├── __init__.py
│       └── merge_adapter.py      # Merge LoRA adapter into base model
├── configs/
│   ├── llama2_7b_qlora.yaml
│   └── mistral_7b_qlora.yaml
├── scripts/
│   ├── train.py                  # Training entrypoint
│   ├── evaluate.py               # Evaluation entrypoint
│   └── push_to_hub.py            # Push merged model to HF Hub
├── data/
│   └── sample/
│       └── clinical_instruct_sample.jsonl
├── docker/
│   └── Dockerfile.train
├── .env.example
├── requirements.txt
└── README.md
```

---

## Quickstart

### 1. Install dependencies

```bash
python -m venv venv && source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 2. Prepare data

Your training data should be JSONL in instruction format:

```json
{"instruction": "Extract all medications from the following clinical note.", "input": "Patient is on Metformin 500mg BID and Lisinopril 10mg QD.", "output": "Medications: Metformin 500mg BID, Lisinopril 10mg QD"}
```

```bash
python scripts/train.py --config configs/llama2_7b_qlora.yaml --data_path data/sample/
```

### 3. Track with MLflow

```bash
mlflow ui --port 5000
# Navigate to http://localhost:5000
```

### 4. Evaluate

```bash
python scripts/evaluate.py --model_path ./outputs/checkpoint-final --test_data data/sample/test.jsonl
```

### 5. Serve

```bash
uvicorn src.serving.inference:app --port 8001
```

---

## Training Config Example

```yaml
# configs/llama2_7b_qlora.yaml
model_name: meta-llama/Llama-2-7b-hf
output_dir: ./outputs/llama2-clinical
dataset_path: ./data/clinical_instruct.jsonl

# QLoRA
load_in_4bit: true
bnb_4bit_quant_type: nf4
bnb_4bit_compute_dtype: bfloat16

# LoRA
lora_r: 16
lora_alpha: 32
lora_dropout: 0.05
target_modules: [q_proj, v_proj, k_proj, o_proj]

# Training
num_train_epochs: 3
per_device_train_batch_size: 4
gradient_accumulation_steps: 4
learning_rate: 2e-4
lr_scheduler_type: cosine
warmup_ratio: 0.03
max_seq_length: 2048
fp16: false
bf16: true

# MLflow
mlflow_tracking_uri: http://localhost:5000
mlflow_experiment_name: clinical-llm-finetuning
```

