## Evaluation Results (Sample)

| Metric | Base Model | Fine-Tuned |
|---|---|---|
| ROUGE-L | 0.41 | **0.61** |
| Clinical NER F1 | 0.53 | **0.81** |
| BLEU-4 | 0.22 | **0.38** |
| BERTScore F1 | 0.74 | **0.87** |

